## Instance methods

### `setTheme(colorOrImage,customColors)`
Sets the theme of the application based on a color or image.

Name | Type | Description
--- | --- | ---
`colorOrImage` | `string` | Hexadecimal color or URL of an image.
`customColors` | `object` | Custom color configurations.


#### Examples
```
// Set them from hex color
setTheme("#6750a4");
```
```
// Set theme from image
const image = new Image();
image.src = "./assets/image.png";
setTheme(image);
```

